HEADWORD: Photobiotic
<hw>Pho`to*bi*ot"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Photo-</ets> + <ets>biotic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
<def>Requiring light to live; incapable of living without light; <as>as,
<ex>photobiotic</ex> plant cells</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

